# ðŸ“ˆ Stock Predictor App

A real-time stock market predictor built with Streamlit.

## Features
- Fetches live stock data via yfinance
- Predicts next 7 days' closing price using Linear Regression
- Interactive Plotly charts
- CSV download of predictions
- Supports multiple tickers

## Live Demo
[Deploy this app on Streamlit Cloud](https://streamlit.io/cloud)

## Usage
1. Input ticker(s), date range.
2. Click `Predict: TICKER`.
3. View data, prediction, and interactive chart.
4. Download CSV if needed.

## Built With
- Python
- Streamlit
- yfinance
- scikit-learn
- Plotly

## Authors
Team of four BE Computer students from SPPU.
